long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
MySafe is a corporate personal and team data manager within senhasegura.
It allows users to securely store and manage their passwords, notes, files and API secrets from apps and online services.

Functionality
It functions as a central hub for privileged information in which users can store corporate personal and team data.
Password protection is the cornerstone of information security. That's why senhasegura developed a product that enables end-users to safeguard their passwords and other data against unwanted third-party access.

Applicability
Protect passwords, documents, notes, and API secrets from leaking.
Create a safe way to share data with team members.
Control and manage access to privileged information.
